graph TD
    AM[ApplicationMaster] -->|1. Resource Request via Heartbeat| RM[ResourceManager / Scheduler]
    RM -->|2. Check Queue Allocation & Limits| Q[Scheduler Queues]
    Q -->|3. Evaluate Locality: Node-Local -> Rack-Local -> Off-Switch| L[Locality Manager]
    L -->|4. Reserve / Allocate Resource| C[Container Allocator]
    C -->|5. Generate Container Token| S[Security / Token Manager]
    S -->|6. Return Container in Heartbeat Response| AM
    AM -->|7. Connect with Token & Launch Command| NM[NodeManager]
